{"tid":1852004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【投票要人】入黎撳個掣，反對丹麥向支那道歉！","createTime":"2020-01-30T09:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:04:50.000Z","uid":250654,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"595e529d7ea68c13f5510f149bacf929b0b14f66","tid":1852004,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpN4exnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpN4exnx.jpg&h=06736267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應唔應該為左呢幅圖而向支那道歉？<br />\n痴撚線梗係唔會！<br />\n而家丹麥報章正進行民意投票應唔應該向支那道歉<br />\n麻煩手足幫手<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">投「唔應該道歉」(Nej)</span></span></strong><br />\n唔可以向極權低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n碌落文章中間就係個投票<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揀Nej</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Nk9Bog.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Nk9Bog.png&h=90cd09ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/indland/ambassadoer-fastholder-krav-om-undskyldning-jp-tegning-hjerteloest-og-egoistisk?from=groupmessage&amp;fbclid=IwAR3-gQcYpxi-LYyZDMmmo2h6pCGsEma8A6CDSUZBeMxrvzMGMkhzqQMrO7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dr.dk%2Fnyheder%2Findland%2Fambassadoer-fastholder-krav-om-undskyldning-jp-tegning-hjerteloest-og-egoistisk%3Ffrom%3Dgroupmessage%26fbclid%3DIwAR3-gQcYpxi-LYyZDMmmo2h6pCGsEma8A6CDSUZBeMxrvzMGMkhzqQMrO7U&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=8d572c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/indland/ambassadoer-fastholder-krav-om-undskyldning-jp-tegning-hjerteloest-og-